===Conjunction===
'''whether'''
# Used instead of [[if]] to express an indirect question
#: I wonder '''whether''' the pubs are open yet?
# Used instead of [[if]] or [[either]] to express alternative possibilities
#: I am going to have a drink, '''whether''' you like it or not.
#: He chose the correct answer, but '''whether''' by luck or by skill I don't know.

